Subject: [PATCH 8/8] arm64: Implement HAVE_DYNAMIC_FTRACE_WITH_CALL_OPS
Date:   Mon,  9 Jan 2023 13:58:28 +0000
Message-Id: <20230109135828.879136-9-mark.rutland@arm.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
